  "text": "To evaluate group homogeneity relative to weight, Student's t test was used for independent samples. Variance analysis of the percentages of nuclei stained with anti-Ki-67 was conducted using the Levene and Student's tests [CITATION_1] . The significance level was set at po0.05.",
